{"tid":2462471,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做左一年RA，愈做覺得自己愈廢","createTime":"2021-03-26T04:27:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T11:43:38.000Z","uid":220804,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f395fcd1c5fbba6712887ce9bb6c43ecb6ddc2b","tid":2462471,"uid":220804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"今年fg，好好彩識人介紹跟左個prof做RA<br />\n初時做都好地地，咁同時有人lead住，可能會有種安心啲感覺。<br />\n做左無耐左後，prof就開始比左個新project我做，要自己諗新idea，design實驗，寫下paper<br />\n已經成4、5個月，都好似唔係好做得出啲野，成個人完全諗唔到野，試左好多野都唔成功，又諗唔到新idea，之後就卡死左，更何況寫paper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見到啲同事好做到啲野出黎，相反自己就坐到個腦都塞L埋，好挫敗<br />\n成日好驚令prof好失望，唔知點交代，壓力好大，開始諗自己仲適唔適合呢個位，又驚比人炒搵唔到工，因為唔算啲咩專科，但我屋企仲對我好大期望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無助個陣就真係辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多謝大家睇完"},{"pid":"6c0324dc704a098207a4468996f46ffdbe9bdcde","tid":2462471,"uid":331590,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"加油呀樓主"},{"pid":"5ea613e9fcab4afd6a42fb6d2c89d7a6763aa4e5","tid":2462471,"uid":375948,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:33:30.000Z","msg":"揀得你即係你係得架啦<br />\n加油啊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb52de8f9a428565e09f5397135f03cad7c1cf4a","tid":2462471,"uid":220804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c0324dc704a098207a4468996f46ffdbe9bdcde","tid":2462471,"uid":331590,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:30:47.000Z","msg":"加油呀樓主"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"好多謝你阿<img s